summary:
This just occurred to me.
So, Peter has officially appeared in three films, right? 
Civil War, Homecoming and Infinity War....
body:
This just occurred to me.

So, Peter has officially appeared in three films, right?

Civil War, Homecoming and Infinity War.

Peter, at sixteen years old, has played an active role in TWO superhero wars.

Against Cap and against Thanos.

I vote that Far From Home is referring to that fact that he’s chilling in, like, Spain or somewhere on a beach with Tony.

Not in peril.

Seriously.

#protectpeterparker2K18
